Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs30\bord0\pos(610,370)\fad(700,1400)}貓不會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美美 給我一杯水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏特加在俄羅斯語裡是水的意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且喝這個燐也比較高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神恢復了的話 就努力工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作要好好做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然每次都有跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶而做個視力檢查會比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟之前一樣沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是度數說不定加深了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那永遠不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掰囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 小燐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到那卡車快要輾到那隻貓時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了躲閃 碰的一聲撞上了油罐車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻貓跑到哪去了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠跑去那邊了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別多說了 跟我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢...這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 這種事要問女生嗎 啊痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不跑沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不喜歡用跑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燐 你不是去找貓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為替代我不是帶了個男的回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就放輕鬆下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當作是自己家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也完全不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那些人會來找碴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對不起 把你牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得如果是你的話似乎可以幫我的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燐從以前就會帶些像這樣有隱情的男人回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是燐小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:08:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是美美 永遠不變喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是喪失記憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是有記憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做前埜光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住址跟電話號碼也能說的出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連昨天吃的晚餐也記得...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是卻沒有實感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 這種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己明明是前埜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻沒那個自信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就好像裝做別人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 關於襲擊你的那些人你心有數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道啊 莫名奇妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來的時候就已經是站在那發呆的那時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美美雖然看起來那樣 其實年紀比你大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連為什麼在歌舞伎町也是沒有真實感的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為我沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得早上出門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後前往大學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來就已經在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又這樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得今天能做好的事拖到明天做可不是很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝完醒來以後 那個奇怪的感覺說不定就治好了囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為這命運的相逢乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾...乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一滴酒可是跟一滴血一樣珍貴喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看的見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定出乎意料的就在附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿醉對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們喝到最後的關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加了白蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對宿醉來說是迎接早晨的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是覺得很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這就是我的真實感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉體方面倒是成長了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出門了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去尋找你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前埜光輝 20歲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上甲大學經濟學系2年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 前埜清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前埜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻沒有在這裡生長的實感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算看到母親也覺得像是看到陌生人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來完全沒在擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我常常什麼都沒說就到朋友那住的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友的家...啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男性的朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕照跟身份證都沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是職業的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業的是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅啊 勒索啊 綁架等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是一群職業的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上山不動產?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 小燐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想來我這工作了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼女王的 我對那沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過妳就是這樣才讓人喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想妳應該知道 很貴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果跟你正在找的女人的所在交換呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我吧 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個酒女...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上山不動產啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在哪聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了啦 我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是哪個與幫派有關係的人經營的企業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個先不說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我那女的所在之處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我想說的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託妳啦 小燐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個酒女欠我很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 這可不是碰面的地...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 給我杯混合咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人看到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是搞婚外情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還單身 你明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳 妳什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇我啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些隱情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於剛剛在電話跟你說到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事 警察怎麼可能能告訴你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 去年年底
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上山不動產雖然在外表是優良中小企業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是血之組的關係企業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是為什麼會是優良企業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能管管這男孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是學校的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可沒從頭開始教起的時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不用管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與血之組有聯繫的企業呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血之組可是跟相當大的企業有聯繫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便出手可是會受傷的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯繫特別深的是不動產企業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炒地皮是他們擅長的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部門的關節什麼的 不清白的勾當什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來就是從外圍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山製藥 富山工業 Sky of Japan等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山製藥...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到什麼線索了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大約一個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得前輩介紹了一份不錯的零工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新藥的實驗什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道這次你要幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都很溫柔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是內山專務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得有個能互相瞭解的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是專務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認證也很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然聽說你不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不是什麼好人所以不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管幾次我都會殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客房服務
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是就放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是拿回去會比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的老闆是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委託人的秘密是絕對不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把我射出的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好人都死得早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 想吃的話冰箱裡面有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到討厭的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.29,0:22:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做些奇怪的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前埜在看著喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎都無法復原
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電子郵件也都損毀 沒法知道內容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過燐帶前埜回來的那天附近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狹山研究所與總公司的電子郵件往來似乎相當頻繁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狹山研究所我一點頭緒都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 要正面進攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信美美的技術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們...那個...該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且因為我的關係把你們牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.18,0:24:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然現在問這有點晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是萬事屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}<什麼委託都接的人>
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.84,0:24:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...報酬什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.99,0:24:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是 我會想看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.68,0:24:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會被發現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.03,0:24:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.69,0:24:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人比照片美多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.03,0:24:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.22,0:24:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼印象
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.25,0:24:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.30,0:24:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.50,0:25:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得朝這直走
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.38,0:25:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 前埜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.38,0:25:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起什麼了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.03,0:25:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那樣子 你在這遇上了什麼事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.25,0:25:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回去的話只有現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.65,0:25:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我問了自己是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.62,0:25:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個答案 或許能在此找到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.15,0:26:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不知道或許比較好也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.68,0:26:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做決定的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.07,0:26:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.95,0:26:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我覺得我不能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.71,0:26:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.76,0:26:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契約成立
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.45,0:26:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 同伴身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.09,0:26:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以讓他在哪休息一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.43,0:26:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.75,0:26:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無關的人員是禁止進入警衛室的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.46,0:26:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會 剛好要檢查的也是這間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.43,0:26:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他好了以後會馬上進行檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.36,0:26:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託囉 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.54,0:26:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以借我煙跟打火機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.90,0:26:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.43,0:26:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 等會一定會還你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.63,0:26:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把完成工作喲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.05,0:26:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.70,0:26:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.72,0:26:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.43,0:26:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.74,0:26:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛的警衛 身上有槍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.97,0:26:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來相當危險喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.55,0:27:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.08,0:27:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依照美美準備的設計圖來看
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.37,0:27:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2樓很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.06,0:27:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 往上走就必須要經過警衛室前面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.01,0:27:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了那之外的路是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.09,0:27:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把剛剛的煙點上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.76,0:28:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.10,0:28:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都別說 不然扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.19,0:28:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.78,0:28:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫山之辺沙耶羅
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.70,0:28:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我沙耶羅就好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.66,0:28:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫沙～耶～羅也行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.62,0:28:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是...啊 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.06,0:28:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正馬上就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.78,0:28:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 妳知道人身上有幾個洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.88,0:28:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛有2個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.15,0:28:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵有2個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:28:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子有2個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.74,0:28:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴有1個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.30,0:29:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來是這裡 有3個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.81,0:29:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是10個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.49,0:29:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過男生只有9個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.89,0:29:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿孔耳環是神所賜與\N讓身上的洞能夠經由人的手改變的東西喲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.88,0:29:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從史前時代開始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.41,0:29:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類就用試著用穿孔耳環擺脫神的創造之手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.51,0:29:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不覺得是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.34,0:29:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合妳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.16,0:29:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是要塞住這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.71,0:29:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以讓妳保持處女之身喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來幫妳一個一個地穿上環
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還有很多其他的事情也要試試
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.83,0:29:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不得了的虐待狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.89,0:29:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.56,0:29:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 已經開始害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.60,0:29:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不要說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.22,0:29:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最開始想聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.54,0:29:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是妳發出的這樣的聲音喔
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.03,0:29:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是第11個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.66,0:30:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.97,0:30:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.78,0:30:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.39,0:30:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新宿發生車禍的油罐車
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.79,0:30:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把前埜...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.93,0:30:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後似乎很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.11,0:30:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那是運送檢體的特殊用車
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.59,0:30:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得要矇騙警察之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.26,0:30:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這些都是那些主公司的笨蛋們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.85,0:31:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫他們要從我這把他搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.78,0:31:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼再繼續下去有違倫理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.52,0:31:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼前埜...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.48,0:31:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.69,0:31:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是克隆體的適合人選
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.53,0:31:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我專長是細菌研究
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.16,0:31:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某種細菌的RNA
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.35,0:31:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與人類的DNA起了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.21,0:31:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現使其產生爆發性增殖的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後將腦內情報轉抄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.42,0:31:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.51,0:31:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要如何辦到?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.82,0:31:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是企業機密
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.00,0:31:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 並不與電子學相關就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.23,0:31:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為情報量太過龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.39,0:31:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是開發軟體好像就得花上一輩子的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.49,0:31:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終歸是以化學的觀點來看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.33,0:31:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做那種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.66,0:31:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要問有什麼好處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是邁向不老不死的一步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.53,0:31:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.11,0:32:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受艾伯斯所擺佈的墮落者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.63,0:32:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.65,0:32:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.14,0:32:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.11,0:32:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是　人類果然是不知吸取教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.22,0:32:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想要變的不老不死的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.38,0:32:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.91,0:32:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自尊心很高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.63,0:32:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惹他生氣會很恐怖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.98,0:32:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是自己的研究被嘲笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.39,0:32:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇 局長也真做得出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.79,0:32:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體無完膚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.07,0:32:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是個美人啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.18,0:32:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然穿了這麼多環
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.20,0:32:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快把她塞進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.42,0:33:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.14,0:33:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你帶到這的人已經死掉囉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.52,0:33:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再離開你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.32,0:33:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管上層說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.32,0:33:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.26,0:34:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.40,0:34:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎還有另一名侵入者的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.66,0:34:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他清除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.61,0:34:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允許開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.90,0:34:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.41,0:34:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.07,0:34:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了自己好 可別去實驗樓B棟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.99,0:34:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就不喜歡跑步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.40,0:34:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.91,0:35:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.90,0:35:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快撤!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.19,0:35:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.33,0:36:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前埜...他是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.43,0:36:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點 說的出話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.55,0:36:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.76,0:36:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攝影機呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.76,0:36:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B棟的攝影機狀況本來就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.33,0:36:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.00,0:36:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費一場難得的好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.86,0:36:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.50,0:36:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.37,0:36:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除P4隔離壁的鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.39,0:37:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們被沙耶羅弄成那樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.40,0:37:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 你們已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.93,0:37:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓你們解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.92,0:38:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B棟的隔離壁居然會被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.85,0:38:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也馬上會受到感染
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.69,0:38:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.35,0:38:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.69,0:38:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毀掉A到C級別的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.07,0:38:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將B棟燒掉後
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.55,0:38:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這裡也燒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.94,0:38:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣做的話 主公司會...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.03,0:38:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說感染力不強
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.88,0:38:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是會擴散的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.81,0:38:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你也想變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.35,0:38:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.62,0:38:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳應該已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.35,0:39:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.09,0:39:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.66,0:39:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.88,0:39:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.81,0:39:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.72,0:39:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.43,0:39:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳想成為的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.15,0:39:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.73,0:39:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.08,0:39:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.93,0:40:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然由我說出來很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.27,0:40:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}求求你 求求你開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.59,0:40:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命是短暫無常的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.41,0:40:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能隨意操弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.52,0:40:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.25,0:40:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.17,0:40:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.46,0:40:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.06,0:40:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克隆人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.16,0:40:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才對任何事物都感受不到真實感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.81,0:40:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.08,0:41:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.50,0:41:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會說什麼我很瞭解你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.28,0:41:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的痛苦是只屬於你自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.72,0:41:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.64,0:41:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會說什麼那只是逃避什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.30,0:41:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是一種獲得救贖的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.67,0:41:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是背負著痛苦活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.90,0:41:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是要逃離痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.21,0:41:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.76,0:41:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.68,0:41:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你這樣跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.46,0:42:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 妳不喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.93,0:42:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以別帶什麼男人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.14,0:42:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把貓帶回來就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.65,0:42:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.73,0:42:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.89,0:42:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.03,0:42:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燐
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.43,0:42:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燐
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.77,0:42:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.12,0:42:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我能繼續過下去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.16,0:43:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 可以讓我在這工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.75,0:43:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錄用啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.97,0:43:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 喝吧 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.60,0:43:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.30,0:43:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.53,0:43:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝啊 慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.39,0:43:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝 慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.22,0:45:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一被留下的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.31,0:45:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就像壞掉的機械般
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.09,0:45:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷重複試著想解開
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.09,0:45:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許應該將那心意懷抱於心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.63,0:45:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受夢之邀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.31,0:45:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向精疲力竭的他要求接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.98,0:45:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.05,0:45:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我必須要殺死他
